Privacy Policy Changes
Although most changes are likely to be minor, Comitic may change its Privacy Policy from time to time, and in Comitic's sole discretion. Comitic encourages visitors to frequently check this page for any changes to its Privacy Policy. Your continued use of our services, including but not limited to our website, mobile applications and our web services after any change in this Privacy Policy will constitute your acceptance of such change.
Questions or Concerns?
If you would like to communicate with us about this Privacy Policy or Comitic’s collection and use of data please contact Comitic at
contact@comitic.com